name: Time machine
description:
This photo I took around my office in the Jl Terusan jakarta area, this is one of my archive photos in 2017.

A very unique and rare moment between a bird that stays on top of a house and an airplane that will land at the airport, 

A very significant difference between a bird that can fly freely and an airplane using a machine that can fly, therefore I give the theme of this photo "Time machine.

I'm so lucky to get this photo.
